.changes
  .container
    .row
      .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1
        .change
          %h2
            = key_display @req_change.changed_key
          %h3 Original Text
          %p
            = @licensed_practice.get_attribute_val @req_change.changed_key

          %h3 New Text
          %p
            = @req_change.changed_val

          .change-buttons
            %button{class: 'btn btn-success'} Accept
            %button{class: 'btn btn-danger'} Deny

        .comments
          .comment-header
            %p Comments
          .comment-container
            .comment
              <span><a href='#'>ASWB Admin</a></span><br />
              Hey Tom, I don't like this change. It has too many words that make no sense. Where did you even get this crazy text? Oh no, I've been infected too!

              Mauris bibendum eu quam quis porttitor. Donec quis dignissim turpis, sit amet aliquet arcu. Sed volutpat risus quis congue molestie. Proin lorem tellus, dapibus quis ultrices ut, faucibus a sem. Donec vitae purus feugiat, vehicula lectus sit amet, pellentesque turpis. 

            .comment
              <span><a href='#'>ASWB User</a></span><br />
